               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Two lines of the incipit of each question and answer; elements of the punctuation signs; Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
&#xD;
A few lines on the incipit page of the text.</rubric>
