                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>- The text consists of a series of questions asked by monks (beginning with ይቤሉ: አኃው) and answers given by an “interpreter” (starting with ይቤ: መተርጕም). The questions are numbered.</note>
                  </msItem>
